<h1>Next Decade, Inc.</h1>
<p style='font-size: 16px'>Next Decade, Inc. is a communications firm that was founded in 1995. Since then we have published dozens of award-winning nonfiction reference books and created communications and marketing programs that simplify complex subjects.</p>

<div style="margin-left: 30px; margin-right: 100px; margin-top: 30px; ">

<p style='font-size: 16px'>

